sequenceDiagram
    participant Saler
    participant SalerWeb
    participant API
    Saler->>SalerWeb: Save POI form
    SalerWeb->>API: POST/PUT /api/poi
    API-->>SalerWeb: POI saved (PendingReview)
    alt Optional TTS
        SalerWeb->>API: POST /api/audio/convert
    else Optional Upload
        SalerWeb->>API: POST /api/audio/upload
        SalerWeb->>API: POST /api/audio
    end
    API-->>SalerWeb: Audio result
    SalerWeb-->>Saler: Success/partial-success feedback
